title: Latvia CPI Housing & Utilities
description: CPI Housing Utilities in Latvia decreased to 170 points in October from 173.10 points in September of 2022. CPI Housing Utilities in Latvia averaged 77.98 points from 1999 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 173.10 points in September of 2022 and a record low of 35.10 points in January of 1999. This page provides - Latvia  Cpi Housing & Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistical Bureau of Latvia
